msgid ""
"Selecting technos, controlled by player, now may show a flash effect by "
"setting `SelectionFlashDuration` parameter. Set "
"`SelectionFlashDuration=0` to disable it."
msgstr ""
"现在可以通过设置 `SelectionFlashDuration` 来让由玩家控制的单位在被选中时可以出现闪烁效果。或 "
"`SelectionFlashDuration=0` 以禁用。"

