msgstr "杂项"

#: ../../User-Interface.md:587
msgid "Skip saving game on starting a new campaign"
msgstr "开始新战役时跳过保存游戏"

#: ../../User-Interface.md:589
msgid ""
"When starting a new campaign, the game automatically saves the game. Now "
"you can decide whether you want that to happen or not."
msgstr "在开始新战役时游戏会自动保存游戏。现在你可以自行决定是否要进行保存。"

